
    Lesson 2 Episode 1 --- commit in a secondary branch
    Please perform the following tasks individually
	    
    1a. Stay in (or go to) branch B2 (the file Lines.txt contains
        eight lines)
    1b. Append a ninth and a tenth line in the usual way
    1c. Make a single commit of these two changes
        Specify the branch name in the commit message!
    1d. Inspect the working tree
    
    Formulate your explanation of what you have observed
    The following questions are two sides of the same coin:
        What did you ask Git to do?
        What did Git do for you?
